      <h2 class="fs-600 uppercase ff-serif">Primary Universe</h2>

      <p>The Primary Universe is the dimension in which we exist under ordinary conditions.<br>
      Sparrow herselfcharacterizes our dimension as being "<i>fraught with great peril</i>".
      However, being the Primary Universe the dimension in which we exist ordinarily, it is our mission to keep it intact.</p>
      

